---
title: Traditional Spaghetti Bolognese with Fresh Salad
description: You can't beat a classic, and our traditional spaghetti Bolognese is here to prove just that! The delicate mixture of tomato, stock, cream, mirepoix and thyme will please your taste buds and warm your soul.
